---
import '../styles/global.css';

const bookingLink = "mailto:hello@systemshift.coach"; // TODO: replace with Cal.com link when ready
const linkedInLink = "https://linkedin.com/in/lukasciszewski";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="Systemic coaching for IT professionals ready to shift. By Lukas Ciszewski — 20+ years in IT, trained systemic coach." />
  <title>SystemShift — Coaching for IT Professionals</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Header -->
  <header>
    <a class="logo" href="/">systemshift.coach</a>
    <div class="lang-toggle">
      <button class="active" id="btn-en" onclick="setLang('en')">EN</button>
      <button id="btn-de" onclick="setLang('de')">DE</button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>
        <span class="en">The system isn&rsquo;t broken.<br>You&rsquo;re just running the wrong one.</span>
        <span class="de">Das System ist nicht kaputt.<br>Du fährst nur das falsche.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="sub">
        <span class="en">Systemic coaching for IT professionals ready to shift.</span>
        <span class="de">Systemisches Coaching für IT-Professionals, die bereit sind zur Veränderung.</span>
      </p>
      <a class="btn" href={bookingLink} target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <span class="en">Book a free discovery call &rarr;</span>
        <span class="de">Kostenloses Kennenlerngespräch buchen &rarr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <p class="en">
        You&rsquo;re senior. You&rsquo;re capable. You&rsquo;ve shipped things most people only read about.
        And still &mdash; something feels off. Maybe it&rsquo;s the burnout you keep patching.
        The promotion that didn&rsquo;t feel like you thought it would.
        The team you lead but can&rsquo;t quite reach.
        The gap between who you are at work and who you want to be.
      </p>
      <p class="de">
        Du bist senior. Du bist kompetent. Du hast Dinge umgesetzt, von denen andere nur lesen.
        Und trotzdem &mdash; irgendetwas stimmt nicht. Vielleicht ist es das Burnout, das du immer wieder patchst.
        Die Beförderung, die sich nicht so anfühlte wie erwartet.
        Das Team, das du führst, aber nicht wirklich erreichst.
        Die Lücke zwischen dem, wer du bei der Arbeit bist, und dem, wer du sein willst.
      </p>
      <p>
        <span class="en">That&rsquo;s not a productivity problem. It&rsquo;s a systems problem.</span>
        <span class="de">Das ist kein Produktivitätsproblem. Es ist ein Systemproblem.</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What is systemic coaching -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>
        <span class="en">What is systemic coaching?</span>
        <span class="de">Was ist systemisches Coaching?</span>
      </h2>
      <p>
        <span class="en">
          Systemic coaching looks beyond habits and goals. It maps the whole system &mdash;
          your role, your relationships, your organization, your identity &mdash;
          and finds where it&rsquo;s stuck. Then we shift it.
        </span>
        <span class="de">
          Systemisches Coaching schaut über Gewohnheiten und Ziele hinaus. Es kartiert das gesamte System &mdash;
          deine Rolle, deine Beziehungen, deine Organisation, deine Identität &mdash;
          und findet heraus, wo es feststeckt. Dann verschieben wir es.
        </span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who it's for -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>
        <span class="en">Who it&rsquo;s for</span>
        <span class="de">Für wen ist das?</span>
      </h2>
      <ul class="list">
        <li>
          <span class="en">Senior engineers and tech leads feeling the ceiling</span>
          <span class="de">Senior Engineers und Tech Leads, die an ihre Grenzen stoßen</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="en">Engineering managers in transition (IC &rarr; lead &rarr; director)</span>
          <span class="de">Engineering Manager in der Transition (IC &rarr; Lead &rarr; Director)</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="en">CTOs and founders carrying too much, alone</span>
          <span class="de">CTOs und Gründer, die zu viel alleine tragen</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="en">Anyone in IT whose work has become their entire identity</span>
          <span class="de">Alle in der IT, deren Arbeit zur gesamten Identität geworden ist</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How it works / Booking -->
  <section id="booking">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>
        <span class="en">How it works</span>
        <span class="de">Wie es funktioniert</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="pricing">
        <div class="pricing-item">
          <span class="label">
            <span class="en">Single session</span>
            <span class="de">Einzelsitzung</span>
          </span>
          <span class="detail">60 min &nbsp;/&nbsp; 130&euro;</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-item">
          <span class="label">
            <span class="en">6-session package</span>
            <span class="de">6er-Paket</span>
          </span>
          <span class="detail">130&euro; / <span class="en">session</span><span class="de">Sitzung</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-item">
          <span class="label">
            <span class="en">Language</span>
            <span class="de">Sprache</span>
          </span>
          <span class="detail">
            <span class="en">German or English</span>
            <span class="de">Deutsch oder Englisch</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-item">
          <span class="label">
            <span class="en">Format</span>
            <span class="de">Format</span>
          </span>
          <span class="detail">
            <span class="en">Video call</span>
            <span class="de">Videogespräch</span>
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href={bookingLink} target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <span class="en">Book your free 30-min discovery call &rarr;</span>
        <span class="de">Kostenloses 30-Min Kennenlerngespräch buchen &rarr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>
        <span class="en">About</span>
        <span class="de">Über mich</span>
      </h2>
      <p>
        <span class="en">
          I spent 20+ years in IT &mdash; as engineer, lead, and leader.
          I know the culture, the pressure, the identity traps.
          I&rsquo;m also a trained systemic coach.
          That combination is SystemShift.
        </span>
        <span class="de">
          Ich habe 20+ Jahre in der IT verbracht &mdash; als Engineer, Lead und Leader.
          Ich kenne die Kultur, den Druck, die Identitätsfallen.
          Ich bin außerdem ausgebildeter systemischer Coach.
          Diese Kombination ist SystemShift.
        </span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer>
    <span class="footer-brand">systemshift.coach</span>
    <div class="footer-links">
      <a href={bookingLink} target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <span class="en">Book a call ↗</span>
        <span class="de">Gespräch buchen ↗</span>
      </a>
      <a href={linkedInLink} target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn ↗</a>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script>
    function setLang(lang: string) {
      document.documentElement.lang = lang;
      document.body.classList.toggle('lang-de', lang === 'de');
      (document.getElementById('btn-en') as HTMLButtonElement).classList.toggle('active', lang === 'en');
      (document.getElementById('btn-de') as HTMLButtonElement).classList.toggle('active', lang === 'de');
      // Persist choice
      try { localStorage.setItem('sc-lang', lang); } catch {}
    }

    // Restore persisted language on load
    (function() {
      let saved: string | null = null;
      try { saved = localStorage.getItem('sc-lang'); } catch {}
      const lang = saved || (navigator.language.startsWith('de') ? 'de' : 'en');
      if (lang === 'de') setLang('de');
    })();
  </script>

</body>
</html>
